title: Riot police clash with activists in Catalonia
description:
As activists pushed for an independent Catalonia, Spanish riot police smashed their way into polling stations. 

Sky's Mark Stone was there and explains what it was like.

SUBSCRIBE to our YouTube channel for more videos: http://www.youtube.com/skynews
